{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"077d92830c","title":"中央批转甘肃省委关于移人就食支援兄弟省建设安排情况的报告","origin":"甘肃省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1325d695ab","index":0,"year":1961,"month":1,"day":11,"articleId":"077d92830c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29ac9f32a4","type":"title","text":"中央批转甘肃省委关于移人就食支援兄弟省建设安排情况的报告","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"cd74670cc5","type":"appellation","text":"甘肃、陕西、青海、辽宁、黑龙江、河南、湖北、江西、浙江、河北、山西、四川、贵州省委、新疆、宁夏、内蒙自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"8c81fda393","type":"paragraph","text":"中央同意甘肃省委一九六一年一月五日“关于移入就食支援兄弟省建设安排情况的报告”，希即按照执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"e2aa077926","type":"paragraph","text":"据最近了解，有以下问题值得各地注意：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"a0b1066e48","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)车厢取暖设备差，沿途有的地方有时不能保证吃饭、喝水。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"25f247f98e","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)有些调入省在职工到达后生活安排尚未落实。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"cd17702989","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为十万余名职工、家属和解放军在寒冬的调动安置，是繁重的政治任务和组织工作，希望沿途有关省、区党委派出得力干部在本省、区境内重要的车站作好政治工作和照料好吃饭、喝水以及疾病治疗工作，保证他们愉快的平安的到达目的地。在目的地要迅速做好安排工作。铁道部应当组织有暖气的专门送人列车。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"5bf5e14138","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央1961年1月11日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"bc9f928bc6","type":"paragraph","text":"(甘肃省档案馆91—4—938卷)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"},{"id":"cb8dcf4198","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c"}],"page":{"id":"516c0a1b81","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"077d92830c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}